<h4 id="cookie-clicker-bot"><em>Cookie Clicker Bot</em></h4>
<h5 id="visit-the-repo"><a href="https://github.com/phedayat/sel_cookie">Visit the repo</a></h5>

<p>Using Selenium in Python, I created a bot that plays the game <a href="https://orteil.dashnet.org/cookieclicker/">‚ÄúCookie Clicker‚Äù</a>. It begins by receiving 1000 clicks immediately. Each click from the script is referred to as a ‚Äúrapid click‚Äù. After the inital clicks, jobs for purchasing upgrades and products are scheduled. In regular intervals, they buy whatever upgrades and products they can given the cookies we have. A small GUI also appears that allows you to begin an arbitrary amount of rapid clicks or quit the bot.</p>

<p>I‚Äôve been able to get this bot to work out of a repl to some degree of success.</p>

